The paper deals with handwritten text recognition and layout analysis, which are topics commonly studied in computer vision (cs.CV) and information retrieval (cs.IR). The proposed method is based on a convolutional neural network, which is a popular technique in deep learning (cs.CL, cs.DL). Lastly, the paper also discusses the challenges posed by Arabic script, which is a language-specific issue that could fall under natural language processing (cs.CL) or machine learning (cs.LG).
